episodes.title: CULTS: THE COOPERITES - GLORIVALE CHRISTIAN COMMUNITY | Accusations Against New Zealand Community
episodes.description:
Hidden in the rolling hills of New Zealand is a Christian Community some may never have heard of. 

This is the home of The Cooperites or Glorivale Christian Community. Here hundreds of people dedicate their lives to God.

But behind the beautiful landscape hides much darker secrets.

This is CULTS: THE COOPERITES - GLORIVALE CHRISTIAN COMMUNITY | Accusations Against New Zealand Community.

Don't forget to subscribe for more content!
